These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, gardening, hiking, sudoku
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking cola and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking cola##7
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Hobby      | hiking  | gardening | sudoku        | board-games |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
3. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, house, indie
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of indie is somewhere between the fan of dubstep and the fan of classical##7
3. the fan of house is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the fan of classical is somewhere between the fan of indie and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| Music-Genre   | house | classical  | indie   | dubstep |

