.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's hobby is writing##7
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

