.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, reading, rock-climbing, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the german is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | drawing   | video-games | reading |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

