.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, grapefruit, orange, pepper
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, nigerian, spanish
1. the argentine is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
4. the spanish is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person eating orange##7
5. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
6. the spanish is on the left or right of the nigerian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | pepper    | cherry   | grapefruit | orange  |
| Nationality   | argentine | nigerian | spanish    | chinese |

