.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, colombian, spanish
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, horse, rabbit
1. the argentine is not the owner of the rabbit##6
2. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the spanish is the owner of the horse##1
4. the colombian is somewhere between the spanish and the american##7
5. the argentine is on the left of the american##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | colombian | argentine | american |
| Pet           | horse   | rabbit    | dog       | hamster  |

