.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, police-officer, scientist, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, pop, r&b, techno
1. the engineer is not the fan of classical##6
2. the scientist is on the right of the engineer##1
3. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the engineer##3
4. the engineer is on the right of the fan of techno##1
5. the scientist is somewhere between the fan of techno and the police-officer##7
6. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | security-guard | engineer | scientist | police-officer |
| Music-Genre   | techno         | r&b      | classical | pop            |

