.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, satire, thriller, western
4 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, rat, snake
1. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the owner of the snake##7
2. the person watching satire movies is not the owner of the rat##6
3. the owner of the mouse is not the person watching thriller movies##6
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
5. the person watching family movies is the owner of the dog##1
6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | satire | thriller |
| Pet           | dog    | mouse   | snake  | rat      |

