4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the fan of rock##2
6. the fan of soul is somewhere between the fan of rock and the person watching documentary movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
