.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, fishing, hiking
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, subway, trike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person driving the bus##6
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | hiking | collecting | filmmaking | fishing |
| Transport   | bike   | trike      | bus        | subway  |

