.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, skydiving, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, freelancer, paramedic
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the paramedic##7
2. the architect is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
3. the paramedic is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the paramedic##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the architect and the freelancer##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | skydiving | sudoku     | drawing     | rock-climbing |
| Job     | paramedic | freelancer | firefighter | architect     |

