2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | ferret    | goldfish | snake     | dog |
| Transport   | quad-bike | scooter  | motorbike | bus |

